This is a demo application for authentication_engine.

We will try to show you:
1) basic use case of authentication engine
2) basic use case of declarative authorization
3) basic use case of state machine
4) how to set up multiple authorization rules
5) basic use case of subdomain-fu and dynamic layout

You can login as:
  login / password / roles
1) root / root / member, admin
2) tony / tony / member, author
3) jacky / jacky / member, reviewer

== Configuration

please add following to your /etc/hosts

  127.0.0.1 rd.localhost ms.localhost aa.localhost

